node.text:
www.jeremyklein.com
my new lum board is out now! this board is 8.5, and hand screened. I drew this graphic based on a scene in the beautiful dreamer urusei yatsura movie. urusei yatsura is one of my favorite animes of all time. thanks for the overwhelming response from everybody about my birthday, if I didn’t get back to you I’m very sorry, it was more of a response than I ever could’ve imagined, I love you all.

node.text: tomorrow monday, july 12 I will turn 50 years old. I will be having a little get together, and I’d like to invite 10 fans to my little party. If you are in the orange county or los angeles area email me or dm me pictures of your board wall or products that you have of mine. I will choose 10 super fans to come. each of you will get a signed board from me. thank you all. email me here: hookupsofficial@gmail.com
